channel.title: Trouble with doors
channel.description: I open client.java and find deletethatobject and i put in the coords of the door and i compile and run and the door is still there! I cant find a way to open it either? Im using deltascape source n client help?

item.title: Trouble with doors
item.dc:creator: @kmansnoob kmansnoob
item.description:
@kmansnoob wrote:

You have to make it so when a player clicks on that object (door), it replaces it with another object. (In this case, the same door, but set it to face a different direction)

The search menu might have something.
